---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Chaos With Clarity | Abby"
  description="Short, honest ideas about ego, experience, and being fully alive — for people who think too much and feel even more."
>

  <!-- ══ HERO ════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       Deep forest green. Giant bleeding coral type. That's the design.
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="hero-word hw-chaos">Chaos</span>
        <span class="hero-with">with</span>
        <span class="hero-word hw-clarity">Clarity</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-foot">
      <p class="hero-tag">Essays · Poetry · Inner Work — Abby</p>
      <nav class="hero-nav">
        <a href="/writings" class="hero-link">Read the writing <span class="arrow">↗</span></a>
        <a href="/join" class="hero-link">Get the letters <span class="arrow">↗</span></a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ STATEMENT ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       Solid coral. Big cream statement. Paw-inc energy.
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="statement">
    <div class="statement-inner">
      <p class="st-label">This space is for you if —</p>
      <h2 class="st-headline">
        You feel it<br/>
        <em>before you<br/>name it.</em>
      </h2>
      <ul class="st-list">
        <li>You're tired of empty motivation and want depth without the jargon.</li>
        <li>You overthink, feel a lot, and secretly like that about yourself.</li>
        <li>You're curious about stillness, but allergic to spiritual performance.</li>
        <li>You want to own fewer things, carry less ego, and experience more life.</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/writings" class="st-cta">Start reading <span>→</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ ABOUT + POEM ════════════════════════════════════════════
       Warm linen. Two columns. Breathing room.
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-grid">

      <div class="about-left">
        <p class="section-label">About this space</p>
        <blockquote class="about-quote">
          "Spreadsheets couldn't answer<br/>the chest ache.<br/>So I write."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="about-body">Nine years of finance — from EY audit rooms to sitting across from founders who had everything and felt nothing — taught me one thing: clarity without depth is just noise with good formatting.</p>
        <a href="/about" class="about-link">About Abby →</a>
      </div>

      <article class="about-poem"
               data-poem-card
               data-title="Unstruck Silence (Anhat Nad)"
               data-date="March 2026"
               data-poem="It starts but never ends,
It is just life, nothing to amend.

Silence is louder than noise,
Once you hear it, it abides.

Anhat Nad, it is said,
The uncreated sound that spreads.
Not from anywhere near or far,
Always present, revealing scars.

Contradiction is life's way of being,
Fighting it is simply fleeing.

Give your heart a pause,
Breathe in and listen to the cosmos.
It enters you and penetrates deep,
Making every restless cell sleep.

I know it sounds absurd,
That is why words feel blurred.

It starts but never ends,
It is just life, nothing to amend.

Empty the weight you carry in your heart,
Just be, and let silence be the start.

A start not of something new,
But something in you you always knew.

You are so small, yet vast the roles you play,
Trying to be more as life slips away.

To be ahead is just a muse,
Your breaths are counted, if you choose to view.

See what you truly hold,
Let go of wanting, and be bold.

Let silence become your home,
Be less, not more.

Be less, not more."
               data-reflection="">
        <p class="section-label" style="color:var(--olive-accent);">Featured Poem · March 2026</p>
        <h3 class="poem-big-title">Unstruck<br/>Silence</h3>
        <div class="poem-lines">
          <p>It starts but never ends,</p>
          <p>It is just life, nothing to amend.</p>
          <p>Silence is louder than noise,</p>
          <p>Once you hear it, it abides.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="poem-read-cta">Click to read in full <span>→</span></p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ NEWSLETTER ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       Back to forest. Big italic Fraunces. One CTA.
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="newsletter">
    <div class="nl-inner">
      <p class="section-label" style="color:var(--olive-accent);">The Letters</p>
      <h2 class="nl-title">
        Honest notes<br/>
        <em>from the middle<br/>of it all.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="nl-body">
        Thoughts I don't share on Instagram or YouTube. Drafts, process,
        questions I'm still figuring out. No spam. No "daily grind" tips.
      </p>
      <a href="/join" class="nl-cta">Get the Letters</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ══ HERO ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100svh;
    background: var(--olive-dark);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 4.25rem; /* nav height */
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 3rem 3rem 0;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    line-height: 0.82;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .hero-word {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(7rem, 20vw, 24rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--olive-accent);
    /* let it bleed off the right edge */
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .hero-with {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    padding-left: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* entry animations */
  .hw-chaos {
    animation: fromLeft 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
  }
  .hero-with {
    animation: fromLeft 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s both;
  }
  .hw-clarity {
    animation: fromRight 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s both;
  }
  @keyframes fromLeft {
    from { transform: translateX(-10vw); opacity: 0; }
    to   { transform: translateX(0);     opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes fromRight {
    from { transform: translateX(10vw);  opacity: 0; }
    to   { transform: translateX(0);     opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* footer bar of the hero */
  .hero-foot {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,236,224,0.12);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.4s both;
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { transform: translateY(1.5rem); opacity: 0; }
    to   { transform: translateY(0);      opacity: 1; }
  }
  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim-dark);
    font-weight: 500;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .hero-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-link {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .hero-link:hover { color: var(--text-on-dark); }
  .hero-link .arrow { transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .hero-link:hover .arrow { transform: translate(2px, -2px); }

  /* ══ STATEMENT ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     Solid coral bg — the whole section IS the colour.
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .statement {
    background: var(--olive-accent);
    padding: 8rem 3rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .statement-inner {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .st-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.26em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,236,224,0.6);
    font-weight: 600;
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    margin-bottom: -2rem;
  }
  .st-headline {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 8vw, 9rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .st-headline em {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(245,236,224,0.72);
  }
  .st-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
  .st-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(245,236,224,0.82);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding: 1.4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,236,224,0.18);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .st-list li:first-child { border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,236,224,0.18); }
  .st-cta {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,236,224,0.4);
    padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .st-cta:hover { border-color: var(--text-on-dark); opacity: 0.75; }

  /* ══ ABOUT + POEM ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .about-section {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 8rem 3rem;
  }
  .about-grid {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .about-quote {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    font-style: normal;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .about-body {
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .about-link {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .about-link:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--olive-accent); }

  /* poem side */
  .about-poem {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--olive-accent);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  }
  .about-poem:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); }
  .poem-big-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .poem-lines {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2.1;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--olive-accent);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }
  .poem-read-cta {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--olive-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ══ NEWSLETTER ════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  .newsletter {
    background: var(--olive-dark);
    padding: 9rem 3rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .nl-inner {
    max-width: 60rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .nl-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .nl-title em {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--olive-accent);
  }
  .nl-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim-dark);
    line-height: 1.9;
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .nl-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--olive-accent);
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 1.1rem 2.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .nl-cta:hover { background: var(--olive-bright); }

  /* ══ RESPONSIVE ════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .statement-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .st-label { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-inner { padding: 2rem 1.5rem 0; }
    .hero-foot { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .statement { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-poem { padding: 2rem; }
    .newsletter { padding: 6rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
